114
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:04,380
We were kind of even.

115
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:06,740
But you didn't let her kill me
last time.

116
00:10:06,900 --> 00:10:07,780
And you also saved me.

117
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:10,900
I distinguish kindness
and hatred clearly.

118
00:10:11,060 --> 00:10:12,260
So I returned you a favor.

119
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:15,140
But your father killed my father.

120
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:16,380
