122
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,980
We're destined not to be friends.

123
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:24,860
Actually, he isn't my father.

124
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:29,740
But he killed my father.

125
00:10:30,980 --> 00:10:31,820
What do you mean?

126
00:10:32,260 --> 00:10:33,260
In short,

127
00:10:34,220 --> 00:10:35,460
