139
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:10,500
This is the key. Go get it if you want.

140
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:17,620
Thanks.

141
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:18,700
My pleasure.

142
00:11:23,260 --> 00:11:23,980
See you.

143
00:11:25,460 --> 00:11:26,500
Wait.

144
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,780
